descriptions.description_input: In the input, you should see...A large grid with many colors, with a 4x3 box of one color.
descriptions.description_output_grid_size: The output grid size...The grid size stays the same.
descriptions.description_output_instructions: To make the output, you have to...Turn everything black except for the 4x3 box of one color.

descriptions.description_input: In the input, you should see...A lot of small colored boxes with a larger one that is of the same color and at least two rows in size
descriptions.description_output_grid_size: The output grid size...Copy the input grid
descriptions.description_output_instructions: To make the output, you have to...Reproduce the larger box that is of one color and has at least two rows.

descriptions.description_input: In the input, you should see... A grid of random colors with a solid block clearly visible.
descriptions.description_output_grid_size: The output grid size... remains the same size.
descriptions.description_output_instructions: To make the output, you have to... copy the size and position of the solid block, so you have the block on a black background.

descriptions.description_input: In the input, you should see...A large pattern set of the same color
descriptions.description_output_grid_size: The output grid size...The grid size remain the same
descriptions.description_output_instructions: To make the output, you have to...reproduce the large pattern with a black back ground
